INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('804', '1', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Personal Injury and Auto Accident Attorneys</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we focus on the following areas of practice:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong> Motor vehicle accident </strong> – Following a car or truck accident, time is of the essence in securing representation and contacting the insurance company and a physician. From there, we do the hard work of advocating for you and resolving your case through negotiation, mediation or litigation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Wrongful death </strong> – Resolving a case involving the loss of a loved one is complex and requires the experience of a seasoned attorney. We team up with various experts to estimate compensation due for your pain and suffering and lost income in the present and future.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Medical malpractice </strong> – If your doctor deviated from the basic standards of care in treating you, we can pursue a medical malpractice claim on your behalf. At Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we will bring in medical experts to identify the problem and help us establish your claim.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Police brutality </strong> – Excessive force can cause serious injury and even death. It is also a violation of your civil rights. We will assist you throughout the entire process of filing and negotiating, or litigating a claim of police brutality.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Divorce and separation </strong> – Maryland and Washington, D.C. have their own laws. Our attorneys have an extensive knowledge of both jurisdictions and provide aggressive representation to clients from any area.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child custody </strong> – Whether you are in Maryland or Washington, D.C., the focus in a child custody case is the best interests of the children. We work hard to ensure you get the time you need to continue to raise your child.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child support </strong> – Child support involves strict calculations involving income, expenses and custody responsibilities. Most disputes concern the validity of the salary of one spouse and the true costs of daycare or health care.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Permanent residency and adjustment of status </strong> – Immigrants who enter the country legally need help in changing their status based on family matters or marriage. We encourage clients to apply immediately, as the process is lengthy.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Business and family immigration </strong> – We help clients secure business visas for temporary or specialty employment that is in high demand. Our immigration attorneys also help family members with permanent residence status.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to the above listed practice areas, we represent clients on slip and fall cases and protective orders.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince George’s Plaza. We are near Prince George’s Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nFor more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced personal injury, family law or immigration lawyer, please contact us.', 'Practice Areas Overview', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'practice-areas-overview', '', '', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=804', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('805', '1', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Personal Injury and Auto Accident Attorneys</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we focus on the following areas of practice:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong> Motor vehicle accident </strong> – Following a car or truck accident, time is of the essence in securing representation and contacting the insurance company and a physician. From there, we do the hard work of advocating for you and resolving your case through negotiation, mediation or litigation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Wrongful death </strong> – Resolving a case involving the loss of a loved one is complex and requires the experience of a seasoned attorney. We team up with various experts to estimate compensation due for your pain and suffering and lost income in the present and future.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Medical malpractice </strong> – If your doctor deviated from the basic standards of care in treating you, we can pursue a medical malpractice claim on your behalf. At Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we will bring in medical experts to identify the problem and help us establish your claim.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Police brutality </strong> – Excessive force can cause serious injury and even death. It is also a violation of your civil rights. We will assist you throughout the entire process of filing and negotiating, or litigating a claim of police brutality.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Divorce and separation </strong> – Maryland and Washington, D.C. have their own laws. Our attorneys have an extensive knowledge of both jurisdictions and provide aggressive representation to clients from any area.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child custody </strong> – Whether you are in Maryland or Washington, D.C., the focus in a child custody case is the best interests of the children. We work hard to ensure you get the time you need to continue to raise your child.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child support </strong> – Child support involves strict calculations involving income, expenses and custody responsibilities. Most disputes concern the validity of the salary of one spouse and the true costs of daycare or health care.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Permanent residency and adjustment of status </strong> – Immigrants who enter the country legally need help in changing their status based on family matters or marriage. We encourage clients to apply immediately, as the process is lengthy.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Business and family immigration </strong> – We help clients secure business visas for temporary or specialty employment that is in high demand. Our immigration attorneys also help family members with permanent residence status.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to the above listed practice areas, we represent clients on slip and fall cases and protective orders.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince George’s Plaza. We are near Prince George’s Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nFor more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced personal injury, family law or immigration lawyer, please contact us.', 'Practice Areas Overview', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '804-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '', '804', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/804-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('806', '1', '2014-02-28 05:52:17', '2014-02-28 05:52:17', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Maryland Car Accident and Semi Truck Injury Attorneys</h2>\r\nImmediately following a car accident, it may not occur to you to contact a lawyer. However, if negligence was involved, you need the type of aggressive advocacy we provide at Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland.<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-807\" alt=\"i-prac-motorvehicleaccidents\" src=\"http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-motorvehicleaccidents.jpg\" width=\"214\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\nIn a split second, your life can change when a car or commercial truck collides into your vehicle. Injuries can result in significant changes to your personal and professional life. Get help in holding the responsible party accountable.\r\n<h3>Time Is of the Essence Following Your Accident</h3>\r\nWe have handled car, truck and motorcycle accident cases that resulted in soft tissue injuries, broken bones, broken necks and even death. Get medical help immediately, then contact Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, as soon as possible. All of our clients must alert their insurance company about the truck or car crash. These are important steps towards a successful resolution of your case.\r\n<h3>Managing Your Case While You Recover From Your Injuries</h3>\r\nWhile you get treatment for your injuries, we communicate with the insurance company regarding your claim. We secure medical records, medical bills and police reports. We bring in accident reconstructionists and other industry professionals to help in our investigation.\r\n\r\nThe insurance company may contact you for a statement. However, they do not have your best interests in mind. We encourage our clients to say nothing and allow us to provide any information related to their case.\r\n<h3>Settlement or Litigation of Your Motor Vehicle Accident Case</h3>\r\nLiability must be established in car accident and truck accident cases. Our objective is to settle your claim without going to court. However, if we feel the best resolution is litigation or you are not satisfied with the offer in settlement, we will aggressively represent you in the courtroom.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince George’s Plaza. We are near Prince George’s Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nFor more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced lawyer regarding an auto wreck or pedestrian accident, please contact us.', 'Motor Vehicle Accidents', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'motor-vehicle-accidents', '', '', '2014-02-28 05:54:14', '2014-02-28 05:54:14', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=806', '0', 'page', '', '0');
