INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('831', '1', '2014-02-28 06:15:22', '2014-02-28 06:15:22', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Prince George\'s County H1-B and Temporary Visa Attorneys</h2>\r\nYour status as a documented immigrant in the United States is not permanent. Modifications based on changes in circumstances occur often, requiring the type of service that we provide at Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland.<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-830\" alt=\"i-prac-permresadjofstatus\" src=\"http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-permresadjofstatus.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"253\" />\r\n\r\nTime is of the essence in applying for permanent residency or an adjustment of status. Depending on the situation, the process can be immediate or it can take a certain amount of time.\r\n<h3>Bringing Married Couples and Families Together</h3>\r\nThe prospect of uniting couples and reuniting families is a rewarding yet complicated part of our immigration practice at Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC. Many immigrants who come to the United States for purposes of work find a spouse here.\r\n\r\nMarriage to a U.S. citizen will result in an immediate permanent resident card. Even marriage to a permanent resident will allow you to enjoy the same status, just not as quickly. Urgency also exists when you are seeking to have your spouse, parents and children under 21 join you in this country.\r\n<h3>Simple or Complex Processes Involved</h3>\r\nWe communicate our knowledge of the law and processes related to it to our clients. Different status requires different lengths of processing times in securing a permanent resident card. We help clients throughout the entire process of changing their status or receiving a permanent resident card.\r\n\r\nThe first step is immediately filing an application. Whether your application will move through the process quickly or slowly, the timing of the application is important. Many times, residents of a certain country are forced to wait.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince George’s Plaza. We are near Prince George’s Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced lawyer, please contact us.', 'Permanent Residency Adjustment Of Status', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '829-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-28 06:15:22', '2014-02-28 06:15:22', '', '829', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/829-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('832', '1', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Hyattsville, Maryland, Immigration and Naturalization Attorneys</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we help overseas clients enter the United States for purposes of contributing to the workforce. Our firm also assists with family immigration matters as well.<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-833\" alt=\"i-prac-businessfamilyvisas\" src=\"http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-businessfamilyvisas.jpg\" width=\"193\" height=\"253\" />\r\n\r\nWhether your job involves a specialty, low skills or no skills, you can apply for a visa. The immigration process may be lengthy, depending on your profession, but we will advocate for you throughout the entire process.\r\n<h3>Challenges in Changing Status With Business Visas</h3>\r\nDoctors, nurses, athletes, entertainers or persons in any job that has a high demand face reduced processing time in securing a business visa. Those types of visas also allow the individual to apply for an adjustment in status. H1-B visas are not of the type whose status can be adjusted.\r\n<h3>Knowledge of Immigration Law and Procedures</h3>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we maintain a thorough knowledge of the laws and regulations established by the Bureau of United States Citizenship and Immigration Services (USCIS). Information is vital when a client comes to our office seeking an answer to an immigration-related inquiry or help securing a visa, especially when they are seeking permanent residency for a spouse or close family member. Whether you are trying to secure a business visa or permanent residency for a family member, we will help facilitate the process and advocate for you until your immigration case is resolved.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince George’s Plaza. We are near Prince George’s Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced family immigration or business immigration lawyer regarding citizenship, a fiancé visa or a work visa, please contact us.', 'Business Family Visas', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'business-family-visas', '', '', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '2014-02-28 06:17:59', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=832', '0', 'page', '', '0');
