INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('924', '1', '2014-01-02 09:36:55', '2014-01-02 09:36:55', '<div>\r\n\r\nHearing the news that you have cancer is extremely upsetting. There are a number of decisions that Maryland residents must make in light of the diagnosis in terms of treatment options. When a doctor makes an error concerning cancer, the results can be devastating. Failure to diagnose cancer can be deadly. On the opposite end of the spectrum, misdiagnosing someone with cancer can also have extreme consequences, as one recent lawsuit illustrates.\r\n\r\nIn March of this year, a man underwent a lung biopsy, and there was also a close examination of a biopsy he previously had. According to the results, the man never had breast cancer – despite being diagnosed earlier. In light of the diagnosis, the man had a mastectomy and chemotherapy, which his lawyer said were extensive and invasive.\r\n\r\nWhat’s more, the patient was correctly diagnosed with melanoma, and all the treatment he received for the breast cancer had no effect on his condition. The man filed a lawsuit against both the hospital and the doctor, citing medical negligence.\r\n\r\nThis individual may have a long road ahead of him, in terms of additional treatment for his current condition. He may also have to heal from the physical and emotional effects of the misdiagnosis. In his case, and in any case in which an individual has been negatively affected by a doctor error, an attorney can help file a claim seeking compensation for damages such as medical expenses and pain and suffering. While money may not undo the harm that was caused, it may help an individual feel justice was served.\r\n\r\n<b>Source: </b>The West Virginia Record, “<a href=\"http://wvrecord.com/news/264938-man-alleges-incorrect-cancer-diagnosis\" target=\"_blank\">Man alleges incorrect cancer diagnosis</a>,” Whitney Brakken, Dec. 17, 2013\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Suit: Cancer misdiagnosis led to unnecessary chemo and surgery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'suit-cancer-misdiagnosis-led-to-unnecessary-chemo-and-surgery', '', '', '2014-02-28 09:38:11', '2014-02-28 09:38:11', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?p=924', '0', 'post', '', '0');
