INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('942', '1', '2013-10-04 09:54:17', '2013-10-04 09:54:17', '<div>\r\n\r\nSurgeons in Hyattsville have to make life and death decisions every single day. One error can have devastating effects. When a patient or a patient’s family member believes that they are the victim of medical malpractice, they may file a lawsuit against the doctor or the hospital.\r\n\r\nA paralyzed man and his wife sued the hospital where he was treated following an automobile accident nine years ago. They also sued the surgeon who made the negligent decision to delay his medical care. While the lawsuit against the hospital was settled, the suit against the orthopedic surgeon went to a jury trial. The man’s wife and caregiver was awarded $550,000. The man, who is a paraplegic, was given $2.3 million.\r\n\r\nAccording to testimony given at the trial, the man’s paralysis is a result of a negligent decision made by his surgeon. He was admitted to the hospital with severed arteries in his forearm and was being prepared for surgery to stop the bleeding. According to the couple’s lawyer, the man’s blood pressure was dangerously low. Despite this, the surgeon ordered a CAT scan on the man’s knee, which delayed his surgery by 30 minutes. As a result of this doctor error, part of the man’s spinal cord died.\r\n\r\nThis man’s entire life is changed due to one doctor’s negligent decision. If you are the victim of hospital negligence, you may be entitled to compensation for your medical bills, pain and suffering, and lost wages. You may want to contact a lawyer to discuss your legal options.\r\n\r\n<b>Source: </b>Myrtle Beach Online, “<a href=\"http://www.myrtlebeachonline.com/2013/09/17/3715546/jury-awards-285-million-in-myrtle.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jury awards $2.85 million in Myrtle Beach area medical malpractice lawsuit</a>,” David Wren, Sep. 17, 2013\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Doctor error leaves man paralyzed after car accident', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'doctor-error-leaves-man-paralyzed-after-car-accident', '', '', '2014-02-28 09:55:39', '2014-02-28 09:55:39', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?p=942', '0', 'post', '', '0');
