INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('952', '1', '2013-08-29 10:01:45', '2013-08-29 10:01:45', '<div>\r\n\r\nWhen Maryland patients are diagnosed with cancer, they aren’t likely to question the doctor’s assessment. However, in rare instances, a doctor’s misdiagnosis leads to unnecessary medical treatments. Fortunately, the legal system can punish physicians who continually make atrocious doctor errors that affect several patients.\r\n\r\nThree years ago, an oncology nurse in Michigan reported that a doctor she worked with had been intentionally misdiagnosing patients with cancer. Believing they had cancer, the oncologist’s patients underwent chemotherapy and other cancer treatments. The number of people who were misdiagnosed with cancer is unknown, but over the course of two years, the oncologist received more than $35 million in Medicare receipts.\r\n\r\nThe oncologist has been arrested on $9 million bond and faces serious health fraud charges. Although his bond was initially set at $170,000, a federal judge decided to raise it because the doctor and his wife have significant financial assets. If he is convicted, the doctor could receive a prison sentence of 20 years. It is unlikely that the oncologist will ever be permitted to practice medicine. The FBI collected the doctor’s medical records so that it could make the case against him, but according to the oncologist’s attorney, the doctor did nothing wrong.\r\n\r\nIt is unknown whether any of the oncologist’s victims are expected to receive compensation for their pain and suffering. Unfortunately, some doctors’ dishonesty can cause patients to lose trust in their doctors. Even in less egregious cases than this one, victims of medical malpractice may want to talk to an attorney.\r\n\r\n<b>Source: </b>New York Daily News, “<a href=\"http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/doctor-held-9-million-bond-misdiagnosing-cancer-medicare-scam-article-1.1428639\" target=\"_blank\">Michigan doctor held on $9 million bond for misdiagnosing cancer patients in Medicare scam</a>,” Trudi Bird, August 15, 2013\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Oncologist faces health fraud charges for misdiagnosing cancer', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oncologist-faces-health-fraud-charges-for-misdiagnosing-cancer', '', '', '2014-02-28 10:02:47', '2014-02-28 10:02:47', '', '0', 'http://odelugo.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?p=952', '0', 'post', '', '0');
